This program reads the file content conversion information from XSD & can be used to convert XML to CSV or flat file or in the reverse direction i.e flat file or CSV to XML. The main method is in Class /src/com/fcc/conversion/ContentConverter.java and it expects parameters XSD as String, Root element name, Conversion type i.e PlainToXML or XMLToPlain, input file as String i.e either flat file or XML, prefix for escpaing numeric XML segment, suffix for escpaing numeric XML segment.
